title: Egyptian players abroad: Amro Tarek still missing Real Betis squad in Spain - Talents Abroad - Sports
text:
(All times Cairo local time, GMT+2)
Friday 23 October
Ali Ghazal (Nacional de Madeira)
The defender was kept on the bench as Nacional played out a 0-0 draw with Boavista in the Portuguese league.
Saturday 24 October
Amro Tarek (Real Betis)
The Egyptian defender is still out of action for Real Betis after missing the 1-1 draw with Granada in the Spain La liga
Sunday 25 October
Mahmoud 'Trezeguet' Hassan (Anderlecht)
15:30 Anderlecht vs. Club Brugge
Mohamed Elneny (Basel)
17:00 Basel vs. Young Boys
Mohamed Salah (AS Roma)
19:00 Fiorentina vs. Roma
Ahmed Hassan "Koka" (Braga)
21:15 FC Porto vs. Braga
